Package: unicorn
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ruby, librack-ruby, libkgio-ruby
Description: Unicorn is an HTTP server for Rack applications.
 Unicorn is designed to only serve fast clients on low-latency,
 high-bandwidth connections and take advantage of features in
 Unix/Unix-like kernels.
